# CODEOWNERS — automatic review requests + merge gating.
#
# GitHub requests review from the matching owner(s) for any changed path. When
# combined with branch protection ("Require review from Code Owners"), this
# enforces that the right person signs off on each area of the platform.
#
# Syntax: <path glob>  <space-separated @owners>
# Later matches win, so order from general -> specific.

# Default owner for everything not matched below.
